name: SHA2_STEP
value:
do { \
		uint32_t T1, T2; \
		T1 = H + BSG2_1(E) + CH(E, F, G) + K[j] + w[j]; \
		T2 = BSG2_0(A) + MAJ(A, B, C); \
		D += T1; \
		H = T1 + T2; \
	} while (0)

name: SHA2_STEPn
value:
do { \
		uint32_t t1, t2; \
		SHA2_MEXP ## n(pc); \
		t1 = h + BSG2_1(e) + CH(e, f, g) \
			+ K[pcount + (pc)] + W[(pc) & 0x0F]; \
		t2 = BSG2_0(a) + MAJ(a, b, c); \
		d += t1; \
		h = t1 + t2; \
	} while (0)

name: SHA2_STEP1
value: SHA2_STEPn(1, a, b, c, d, e, f, g, h, pc)

name: SHA2_STEP2
value: SHA2_STEPn(2, a, b, c, d, e, f, g, h, pc)
